{"tid":1772644,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】12.8 科大周同學追思會 | 日製UZU純素眼線筆 |  12.8 民陣國際人權日遊行","createTime":"2019-12-06T19:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T03:13:17.000Z","uid":279356,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ee621353a40ebe7e3786230895e3cd3231f4bbad","tid":1772644,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T19:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ReTvuqr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FReTvuqr.gif&h=d9f2a589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqpFRKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqpFRKH.jpg&h=c576d6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔見有美容台所以開係潮流台<br />\n原諒我幾個話題炒埋一碟<br />\n事關 P 牌一日只能開一 po<br />\n最近終於搵到<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">日製純素眼線液</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>cruelty-free</strong></span> alcohol free<br />\n$120@ 入手了啡同黑<br />\n未試唔知會唔會溶得勁<br />\n睇press release係溫水可卸同long last<br />\n應該係MOTELINER既升級版?<br />\n急不及待share係因為<br />\n我成日想將抗爭融入生活呢個想法推己及人<br />\n推多d性價比高既野刺激大家罷買國產product<br />\n同時做記錄以便日後推介比光時入貨<br />\n真香港人要支持光時呀呀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然未試過呢支但超油眼既我向來打底好足<br />\n同埋都多人讚<br />\n所以對佢都有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無絲打用緊分享下<br />\n----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bktn4YN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbktn4YN.gif&h=1ef519ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a01970327b0ca0ca2ed60d70855d5850ff10733d","tid":1772644,"uid":27088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T20:10:00.000Z","msg":"係邊度買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1